<template>
  <DxPieChart :data-source="data" :animation="false">
    <DxSeries argument-field="name" value-field="value">
      <DxLabel :visible="true" :customize-text="customizeText">
        <DxConnector :visible="true" :width="1" />
      </DxLabel>
    </DxSeries>
    <DxLegend :visible="false" />
  </DxPieChart>
</template>
<script>
import DxPieChart, {
  DxSeries,
  DxLabel,
  DxLegend,
  DxConnector
} from "devextreme-vue/pie-chart";

export default {
  components: {
    DxPieChart,
    DxSeries,
    DxLabel,
    DxLegend,
    DxConnector
  },
  props: {
    data: {
      type: Array,
      default: () => []
    }
  },
  methods: {
    customizeText(pointInfo) {
      return `${pointInfo.argument[0].toUpperCase()}${pointInfo.argument.slice(
        1
      )}: $${pointInfo.value}M`;
    }
  }
};
</script>
